name: Brenda
description: After her travels in South Africa near places such as Dyer Island, Quoin Rock Island, Duiwenhoksriviermond Private Nature Reserve, Brenda traveled north along the coast up to Mozambique. Tragically in October of 2012, she was captured in a gill net and killed. To read the press release please copy and paste the following link into your browser: http://bit.ly/VlFfu8
